subproject.corporate outcome: Electoral laws, processes and institutions strengthen inclusive participation and professional electoral administration
subproject.description: Under this project UNDP, the Ministry of Home Affairs and other actors will be implementing activities to ensure that elections are carried out efficiently. This project will assist in the funding of the costs of the necessary external experts/trainers. The project will also foresee in supporting OKB in its role of independent verification of the various electoral processes.
subproject.title: Support to Sur Elections 2010
